OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773187388
OL,3,CMail Editor claims she kept Princess
OL,4,Cof Wales' pregnancy a secret for days
OL,6,FA High Court trial heard that a Mail
OL,7,Fon Sunday editor knew of the Princess
OL,8,Fof Wales' first pregnancy before the
OL,9,Fnews was announced, but chose not to
OL,10,Fpass on the information to "maintain
OL,11,Fher friendships" and not "cross the
OL,12,Fline".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
