OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773187388
OL,3,CMail Editor claims she kept Princess
OL,4,Cof Wales' pregnancy a secret for days
OL,6,FCharlotte Griffiths, Editor at Large
OL,7,Fof the Mail on Sunday, gave evidence
OL,8,Fon Tuesday at the privacy trial
OL,9,Fbrought by seven people, including
OL,10,FPrince Harry, against Associated
OL,11,FNewspapers Limited (ANL), publisher of
OL,12,Fthe Daily Mail and Mail on Sunday,
OL,13,Fover alleged unlawful information-
OL,14,Fgathering.
OL,16,FGriffiths claimed she socialised in
OL,17,Fsome of the same circles as the Prince
OL,18,Fof Wales and the Duke of Sussex, and
OL,19,Fdenied ever hacking a phone or using a
OL,20,Fprivate investigator.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773187388
OL,3,CMail Editor claims she kept Princess
OL,4,Cof Wales' pregnancy a secret for days
OL,6,FANL has strongly denied wrongdoing and
OL,7,Fis defending the claims brought by the
OL,8,Fgroup, which also includes Sir Elton
OL,9,FJohn, David Furnish and Liz Hurley,
OL,10,Fand Baroness Doreen Lawrence.
OL,12,FThe court was told that Griffiths
OL,13,Fbecame aware of the Princess of Wales'
OL,14,Ffirst pregnancy after Prince William
OL,15,Ftold friends Kate had morning sickness
OL,16,Fat a country party she was attending.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773187388
OL,3,CMail Editor claims she kept Princess
OL,4,Cof Wales' pregnancy a secret for days
OL,6,FIn her witness statement, she said: "I
OL,7,Fdraw a line between my professional
OL,8,Fand own personal social life, as
OL,9,Fcompared to my attending events as a
OL,10,Fjournalist."
OL,12,FShe added: "For example, friends
OL,13,Finvited me to a country weekend in the
OL,14,Flast week of November/first weekend of
OL,15,FDecember 2012 which both Prince
OL,16,FWilliam and Kate Middleton were also
OL,17,Fexpected to attend.
OL,19,F"William arrived solo on the Friday
OL,20,Fand explained that Kate was suffering
OL,21,Fwith morning sickness.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773187388
OL,3,CMail Editor claims she kept Princess
OL,4,Cof Wales' pregnancy a secret for days
OL,6,F"The fact that she was pregnant with
OL,7,Ftheir first child would have been big
OL,8,Fnews and St James's Palace only
OL,9,Fconfirmed it the following Monday
OL,10,Fbecause she had to be admitted to
OL,11,Fhospital.
OL,13,F"I decided to keep it to myself.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773187388
OL,3,CMail Editor claims she kept Princess
OL,4,Cof Wales' pregnancy a secret for days
OL,6,F"Geordie (Greig, then editor) found
OL,7,Fout that I had known and was quite
OL,8,Fannoyed that I hadn't reported it to
OL,9,Fhim on the Friday ahead of the palace
OL,10,Fstatement on the Monday ,as we would
OL,11,Fhave scooped the rest of the press,
OL,12,Fbut it was information I had learned
OL,13,Fat a private event and that I was
OL,14,Fattending in a personal capacity so I
OL,15,Ftreated it as such.
OL,17,F"I missed a scoop to maintain my
OL,18,Ffriendships and because I knew where
OL,19,Fthe line was and had decided not to
OL,20,Fcross it."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773187388
OL,3,CMail Editor claims she kept Princess
OL,4,Cof Wales' pregnancy a secret for days
OL,6,FGriffiths also told the court she had
OL,7,Finteracted socially with Prince Harry
OL,8,Fa few times, including one occasion
OL,9,Fwhen the two of them attended a party
OL,10,Fwhere Harry allegedly stayed up all
OL,11,Fnight before having to attend an event
OL,12,Frelated to Trooping the Colour the
OL,13,Fnext morning.
OL,15,FIn her witness statement, she said: "I
OL,16,Fhave been told that call records show
OL,17,Fa call at 2.50am and three text
OL,18,Fmessages at 10.11 being exchanged by
OL,19,Fme and Prince Harry on June 9 2012 and
OL,20,Fasked whether I remember what that was
OL,21,Fabout.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773187388
OL,3,CMail Editor claims she kept Princess
OL,4,Cof Wales' pregnancy a secret for days
OL,6,F"I have never hacked or tapped a
OL,7,Fphone. The records I have been shown
OL,8,Fhad nothing to do with a story or my
OL,9,Fjob."
OL,11,FShe added that she could not initially
OL,12,Fremember how she got Harry's phone
OL,13,Fnumber, but later remembered that he
OL,14,Fsent her his number on Facebook in
OL,15,F2011.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773187388
OL,3,CMail Editor claims she kept Princess
OL,4,Cof Wales' pregnancy a secret for days
OL,6,FMs Griffiths continued: "I do remember
OL,7,Fthat around that date (of the text
OL,8,Fmessages) I had been out at a club
OL,9,Fnight with our mutual friend, Arthur,
OL,10,Fwho then invited me back to his house
OL,11,Ffor an after party."
OL,13,FShe added: "He told me that Prince
OL,14,FHarry would let me in if I made it
OL,15,Fthere first. The music was loud and
OL,16,Fthey didn't hear the doorbell, so
OL,17,FArthur advised me to call and text to
OL,18,Fbe let in.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773187388
OL,3,CMail Editor claims she kept Princess
OL,4,Cof Wales' pregnancy a secret for days
OL,6,F"That particular night stuck in my
OL,7,Fmind as I remember it was around the
OL,8,Ftime of the Trooping of the Colour and
OL,9,Fwe all thought it was quite funny that
OL,10,FPrince Harry had stayed up all night
OL,11,Fand said he had to go to that or
OL,12,Fsomething related in the morning."
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
