OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773187388
OL,3,CMail Editor claims she kept Princess
OL,4,Cof Wales' pregnancy a secret for days
OL,6,FHe is due to continue giving evidence
OL,7,Fon Wednesday.
OL,9,FThis is the Talking Royals - our
OL,10,Fweekly podcast about the royal family,
OL,11,Fwith ITV News Royal Editor Chris Ship
OL,12,Fand Producer Lizzie Robinson...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/14
